song.title: U need me Luvin
song.info:
a song i've made with renoise for a 64kb tracker compo, which i've also won.
This is a very old remix mod i've done back then in 96 or 98 on amiga for the unda50k disk of phase'd.
unluckily the disk never made it. so i've pumped the mod into renoise and pimped it abit. all are 8bit samples. 5 new, rest from back then. 38kb of samples, no vstis.
everything else is musical knowledge and handling of renoise!
